repository-code: "https://github.com/thewonderofyou777z-dot/tjoe-tooltraceeval"
url: "https://thewonderofyou777z-dot.github.io/tjoe-tooltraceeval/"
abstract: "TjoeEvalKit is tjoe's local offline AI agent evaluation toolkit for provided or synthetic trace expectations, approval boundaries, forbidden actions, regression cases, output normalization, and AI answer visibility. It is not a hosted SaaS, dashboard, runtime trace collector, SDK instrumentation layer, live tool caller, web browser, or safety certification system."
